translation.key: The people in your dream seem powerful and important, not at all like the people you know at the small fishing village. How did the dream end? You long to find out...

translation.key: The nightmare fatigues you greatly, your thoughts fractured and sluggish. You're relieved that the terrible dream was only just that, but you regret not being able to see it to its end.
translation.value: 噩梦使你非常疲惫，你的思想支离破碎，迟钝。你松了一口气，可怕的梦只是这样，但你后悔没能看到它的尽头.

translation.key: "Well, what really happened to Brian," Bentley mutters, pressing down on a bleeding wound.
translation.value: "在Brian身上到底发生了什么？Bentley咕哝着，并且按压着流血的伤口。.

translation.key: <bot_23> grins when you hand him the <item_33>s.
translation.value: <bot_23> 释怀地笑了当你把 <item_33> 给了他.

translation.key: Hey..what's <bot_9> up to? Have you...have you talked to her, by chance?
translation.value: 嘿...这是 <bot_9> 怎么回事？你有...你有没有偶然的和她说话?

translation.key: Someone once told me friendship is magic. That's ridiculous. You can't turn people into frogs with friendship
translation.value: 有人曾告诉我友谊即是魔法，真他妈好笑，你怎么可能用友谊把别人变成青蛙

translation.key: Bentley grinds his teeth, clearly in immense pain. Beebis rests his feathered head on your shoulder as though he, too, is concerned.
translation.value: Bentley咬牙切齿，显然非常痛苦。Beebis把他长满羽毛的头靠在你的肩膀上，好像他也很关心你。

translation.key: "It's Brian. I just don't know what he's up to. I just saw him dragging a child deep into the forest. I approached him; I never thought he'd attack me so viciously."
translation.value: "是Brian，我就是搞不懂Brian想干什么。我刚看到他拖着一个孩子进了森林深处。我走近Brian，我从没想过他会这么激烈地对我发起攻击。."

translation.key: "You explain why Beebis is following you, then inquire about Bentley's injuries.
translation.value: "你解释了为什么Beebis要跟踪你，然后关心Bentley的伤势如何。

translation.key: "Beebis? Why is Elena's house ostrich here with you?" Bentley clutches his bleeding wound, staring into Beebis's beady eyes.
translation.value: "Beebis?为什么Elena家的鸵鸟和你在一起?Bentley紧握着他流血的伤口，盯着Beebis亮晶亮的眼睛。

translation.key: "You hand the package to Bentley and explain why you've come. He winces as he listens to you; you quickly realize he has been badly injured.
translation.value: "你把包裹交给了并Bentley解释你来的原因。他听你说话的时候会疼的缩起身子;你很快就意识到他受了重伤.

translation.key: "Not long ago, a teenaged boy named Brian came looking for Elena. Just like you, he also had a spirit with him."
translation.value: "不久前，一个名叫的Brian少年来找Elena，他也有着像你这样的勇气。"

translation.key: "There's something in it for you, too. This friend of mine has been hunting here for ages, so he knows this forest like the back of his hand. Perhaps he can help you find Brian."
translation.value: "这对你也有好处，我有一位朋友打猎于这一块有一段时间了，所以他来到了这片森林就像回到了家，也许我的那位朋友能帮你找到Brian"

translation.key: "I'd like to ask you to send this package to my friend Bentley on my behalf. It's just some dried food he asked me to buy for him several days ago. Though the other items were destroyed, this will prevent him from going hungry, at least."
translation.value: "请你以我的身份我把这个包裹寄给我的朋友Bentley 。里面只是几天前他让我给他买的干粮。虽然其他东西都被毁的一干二净，但这至少可以防止他饿肚子。"

translation.key: "<player>, I'm afraid I need to ask you for another favor." Larry rummages through the scattered goods and fishes out a package.
translation.value: "<player>, 恐怕，我还得请你帮我一个忙，Larry在一地的包裹中翻来翻去，找出一个包裹

translation.key: Glad you're here to help. I couldn't move all this stuff on my own. I'm Larry, by the way, and I'm a traveling merchant." He sticks out his hand. You shake it gamely, then introduce yourself to him.
translation.value: 你能来帮忙太好了，我一个人怎么也搬不动这些东西，顺便说一下，我叫Larry，是个旅行商人 。Larry把手伸了出来，你鼓起勇气跟他握了握手，并介绍了自己

translation.key: "Luckily, we only lost one box of food," Larry grunts.
translation.value: "真幸运, 我们只丢了一盒食物," Larry 嘟囔道.

translation.key: You help shove the scattered crates back to Larry's side.
translation.value: 你帮Larry将散落的箱子推回到她的身边

translation.key: A lot of tenacity and a little bit of luck can go a long way...
translation.value: 坚韧不拔的性格和一点点幸运就能可以让你走得很远...

translation.key: "Even a small, quaint fishing village like this isn't really safe," Willie mutters sadly.
translation.value: "即使是这样一个古朴的小渔村也不会真的安全," Willie难过地嘟囔.

translation.key: "What? You don't know? Well, what can I do? I need to be compensated for this!" Larry roars, frustrated.
translation.value: "啥？你不道? 那我能干啥? 我需要为此获得补偿！" Larry 沮丧地叫.

translation.key: "Brian, Brian... oh, yeah, the crazy jerk who broke my wagon, right? He smacked me! With his hand!" Larry whines.
translation.value: "Brian, Brian... 哦，对，那个弄烂我的马车的死混蛋吗？他给我了个大比兜！" Larry抱怨道

translation.key: "Ugh, why does stuff like this always happen to me?" he groans with a heavy sigh.
translation.value: "呃，为什么这些破事老发生在我身上" 他深沉地叹息道

translation.key: "But before meeting with him, could you help me drive the Sunbirds out of here? They keep stealing our fruit!"
translation.value: "但在遇到他之前，你能帮我把太阳鸟赶走这里吗? 他们一直在偷我们水果"

translation.key: "You really want to know where he is? He's as crazy as the day is long; he's been attacking residents! A couple beans short of a chili, if you know what I mean. If you want to investigate, you can talk to Larry, a traveling merchant. He's the person Brian most recently attacked."
translation.value: "你真的想知道他在哪？他是个疯子，他攻击了这的居民，几个豆子小于一个辣椒，如果你懂我的意思，如果你想调查，你可以去问问Larry，一个旅行商人，他是Brian最近才攻击的人。"

translation.key: You shake your head fiercely. "I have an urgent issue, and I must speak to him to clear things up."
translation.value: 你猛摇头 "我有个紧急的问题必须和他说清楚"

translation.key: "Why are you looking for Brian, too? Do you know him?"
translation.value: "你为啥也找Brian？你认识他？"

translation.key: "He firmly believed he was cursed by an evil spell, so he wanted to ask Elena for help. But the next day..."
translation.value: "他坚信她被邪恶的魔法诅咒了, 所以他要找Elena帮助. 但是第二天..."

translation.key: "I'm sorry. I know it's not your fault. I just need to calm down." He sighs again.
translation.value: "我很抱歉。我知道这不是你的错，我只是需要冷静下来。" 他又长叹一口气

translation.key: "Hmm, <player>, it looks like you'll have to take Beebis with you. Perhaps he can serve as your mount for now. Elena won't mind if you take him out for a trip, I'm sure!"
translation.value: "呃 <player>, 看起来你要带上Beebis在你身边了，也许他可以暂时作为你的坐骑 ，Elena不会见意你带他出去旅行的，我确信！"

translation.key: When you turn to leave, Beebis grabs your sleeve with its beak and gently pulls you back.
translation.value: 当你转身离开时，Beebis用他的喙抓住你的袖子，轻轻地把你拉回来.

translation.key: You nod, planning to ask Willie directly.
translation.value: 你点头，打算直率地去问Willie

translation.key: "Brian fled to the forest. The village garrison is investigating this case right now. Maybe Garrison Member Willie will have some clues."
translation.value: "Brain逃到森林里。村里的驻军正在调查这个案子。也许卫戍队员Willie会知道一些线索。"

translation.key: Worrying that you might end up like Brian, you tentatively ask what happened to him next.
translation.value: 担心你可能会像Brain一样，你小心的向他询问接下来会发生什么.

translation.key: "It's clear that Beebis doesn't see you as a dangerous person."
translation.value: "显然Beebis并没有把你当做一个危险人物"

translation.key: "Brian's personality completely changed. He shattered everything in Elena's place and snapped her staff in two... I'm telling you this because you must stay vigilant."
translation.value: "Brian的性格完全变了. 他打碎了Elena家里的所有东西，还把她的手杖掰成了两半... 我告诉你这些是因为你必须保持警惕。"

translation.key: "How annoying. The most important parts have flaked off. Who knows what was predicted here?"
translation.value: "真是讨厌. 最重要的一部分已经剥落了. 谁知道这代表了什么？"

translation.key: "It means that a hero who will save the world will be born here. But it also says... the hero could become a demon that could destroy the very fabric of our universe."
translation.value: "这意味着一个拯救世界的英雄将在这里诞生。但它也警示…英雄可能会变成恶魔，摧毁整个宇宙的结构."

translation.key: "Do you really want to know?" Flower looks at you, eyes welling with anxiety and fear.
translation.value: "你真的想知道吗?Flower看着你，眼里充满了焦虑和恐惧.

translation.key: Your heart races anxiously; you ask Flower about the message on the stone statue.
translation.value: 你的心急得直跳;你问Flower关于石像上的信息.

translation.key: "Ah, it fits together like a puzzle! I can finally decipher the message inscribed in the statue!" Flower claps gleefully.
translation.value: "啊，就像拼图一样!我终于能破译刻在雕像上的信息了!Flower高兴地鼓掌起来。

translation.key: "Well, at least we found most of the fragments. Let me see. This part should go here, and that one must be placed there..."
translation.value: "至少我们找到了大部分碎片。让我看看。这部分应该放在这里，那部分必须放在那里……"

translation.key: You hand everything you've found, including the Relic Fragments, Flower. You also give her the secret translation information.
translation.value: 你交出你找到的所有东西，包括圣物碎片，花。你还要把秘密翻译信息给她

translation.key: Rusty Rake
translation.value: 生锈的耙子

translation.key: "Beebis, stop following <player>. You're only causing trouble!" Flower shouts, frustrated.
translation.value: "Beebis, 别再尾随 <player> 了！你只会惹麻烦!Flower沮丧地喊道。

translation.key: Well.
translation.value: 很好.

translation.key: "Beebis, come here. Don't get in <player>'s way!" Flower drags Beebis back.
translation.value: "到这里来。不要挡 <player> 的路!Flower拉着Beebis回去。.

translation.key: You nod and prepare to set out. Beebis trots behind you eagerly.
translation.value: 你点点头，准备出发。Beebis在你身后急切地小跑着.

translation.key: "You want to take on that beastly thing? He dwells in the Ruins Cave not far from here, but you'd better be careful."
translation.value: "你想和那个禽兽较量一下吗?他住在离这里不远的废墟洞里，但你最好小心点。"

translation.key: It sounds like the first choice would be much quicker. You ask Flower where you could find the Ruins Giant.
translation.value: 听起来第一种选择要快得多。你问Flower在哪里可以找到废墟巨人。

translation.key: "I suppose you're right. I have two choices. I can defeat the Ruins Giant that stole the translation information... Or I can spend a few days retranslating the ancient spells in Navea."
translation.value: "我想你是对的。我有两个选择。我可以打败窃取翻译信息的废墟巨人……或者我可以花几天时间在 Navea 重新翻译古老的咒语."

translation.key: The usual rusty rake.
translation.value: 常见且生锈的耙子

translation.key: Beebis takes a step back, then quickly catches back up with you.
translation.value: Beebis后退了一步，然后很快又追上了你.

translation.key: You tell Flower everything that happened and beg for assistance.
translation.value: 你把发生的一切都告诉Flower并向他索取帮助。

translation.key: You find small mounds all around the place. Broken pieces of slate are buried beneath them. You report your findings to Flower.
translation.value: 他妈的，这里到处都是土堆，碎片全鸡巴埋在这下面了，这他妈的，服了，艹。你，去把你的发现报告给Flower.

translation.key: "This is useless! There is no translation book for ancient spells. I can't possibly decipher all these. Heck, these runes aren't even complete! Some of them are mostly worn off."
translation.value: "这根本没什么用!古代咒语没有译本。我不可能破译所有这些。真是服了，这些符文都不完整!有些甚至已经磨损了."

translation.key: Beebis continues to stay by your side, watching your every move. It seems very interested in the Light Orb.
translation.value: Beebis 继续在你身边，监视你的一举一动。他似乎对光球很感兴趣.

translation.key: You peer at the runes as Flower taps her feet impatiently.
translation.value: Flower不耐烦地轻拍着脚，你盯着符文看.

translation.key: "Ugh, forget it. I have far more important things to do." Flower sighs, giving up on Beebis. She returns to studying the runes on the Stone Statue.
translation.value: "算了，算了吧!我还有更重要的事要做。Flower叹了口气，放弃了Beebis。她继续研究石像上的符文.

translation.key: Flower calls out again, but Beebis pays no attention. It continues pacing around you.
translation.value: Flower又喊了一声，但Beebis没有注意。它继续在你周围踱步.

translation.key: "This is Beebis, one of Elena's ostriches. He's a bit shy..."
translation.value: "这是Beebis,Elena的其中一只鸵鸟. 他有些害羞..."

translation.key: "Hey, Beebis, come!" Flower tries to pull the ostrich closer, but it ambles away toward you.
translation.value: "嘿, Beebis, 来这儿!" Flower尝试把鸵鸟拉近些, 但它慢慢走向你.

translation.key: As you speak, the Blue Light Orb appears as though it's listening to what you have to say, hanging onto every word, as it dances around you.
translation.value: 如你所说, 当它围着你跳舞时,Blue Light Orb看起来在听你说什么, 不放过一个词.

translation.key: Just as you are about to speak, a black shadow suddenly races over to you. Both you and Flower shriek in surprise.
translation.value: 就在你正要说话的时候，一个黑影突然向你跑过来。你和 Flower 都惊讶地尖叫起来.

translation.key: "I'm so glad you're here to help! Otherwise, I'd never be able to decipher these runes."
translation.value: "我很高兴你能来帮忙!否则,我永远无法破译这些符文."

translation.key: You tell Flower that you have cleared away the Fairies.
translation.value: 你告诉 Flower 你把那些仙灵赶走了.

translation.key: "These are all old runic letters, but whoever etched them upon the stone probably didn't want others to decipher his message easily. This must be the reason..."
translation.value: "这都是些古老的符文字母，但刻在石头上的人可能不想让别人轻易破译他的信息.一定是这样..."

translation.key: "First, I need you to help me get rid of those pesky Petal Fairies and Green Fairies. Only then can I freely search for clues about the stone statue."
translation.value: "首先，我需要你帮我除掉右边那些讨厌的花瓣仙子和绿仙子。只有这样，我才能自由地寻找石像的线索."

translation.key: "Something happened a while ago. Elena needed me to decipher the Runic letters on the statue. She said it was urgent, but she never explained why. However, her request has proven excessively difficult. The first time I translated the spell, it was stolen. Now the Fairies nearby won't let me anywhere near the Stone Statue."
translation.value: "刚才发生了一件事. Elena 要我破译雕像上的符文字母.她说事情紧急，但没说为啥。然而，她站着说话不腰疼.我第一次翻译咒语时，它被仙灵偷走了.现在，附近的仙灵们不让我靠近石像."

translation.key: Hearing that the same thing had happened to Flower sparks hope in your heart. However, you notice that she is focused on the machine in your hands.
translation.value: 听到 Flower 也遭遇了同样的事，你心中燃起了希望.然而，你注意到她专注于你手中的机器.

translation.key: "If I can help you, I'm more than willing to do so. I've seen something like this before. There was a spirit - a Light Orb - following me, but..."
translation.value: "如果我能帮你，我非常乐意。我以前见过类似的情况.有一个灵魂 - 一个光球 - 跟着我，但是……"

translation.key: You immediately ask <bot_23> what's going on.
translation.value: 你火速问 <bot_23> 发生什么事了.

translation.key: "You, too..." <bot_33> murmurs to herself as she stares at the Light Orb.
translation.value: "你也是..." <bot_33> 盯着光球喃喃自语.

translation.key: You appear in front of <bot_33>. The look on her face betrays an overwhelming sense of horror.
translation.value: 你出现在 <bot_33> 面前. 她脸上的表情流露出一种强烈的恐惧感.

translation.key: "Originally, there was some sort of connection between these Runic letters. I don't know why I didn't think about that before," <bot_33> muses, her head in her hands.
translation.value: "这些符文字母之间有某种联系. 我不知道为什么之前没想到," <bot_33> 双手抱头沉思.

translation.key: All I can say is, <player>, um... don't worry... Just get yourself to the Statue Ruins right away. There, you'll find the Witch's Assistant, <bot_33>. Perhaps she can help.
translation.value: 我只能说, <player>, 嗯…别担心…赶快去雕像遗址吧。在那里，你会找到女巫的助手 <bot_33>. 也许她能帮上忙.

translation.key: A moment of awkward silence passes, and then... <bot_23> -- thinking carefully -- lets out a long breath.
translation.value: 一阵尴尬的沉默过去了，然后…… <bot_23> --仔细思考 -- 深深地吸了一口气.

translation.key: I don't understand. I've never seen anyone react this way to my medicine. A possible allergy... no... impossible! I'm just as interested in finding out what's going on as you are!
translation.value: 我不明白.我从没见过有人对我的药有这种反应.可能是过敏…不…不可能!我和你一样想知道到底发生了什么!

translation.key: This... is just a bottle of <item_45>. It couldn't do something like this...
translation.value: 这，这只是一瓶 <item_45>. 它不可能起这种作用...

translation.key: You nervously explain to <bot_18> that you know nothing about medicine, and you don't want to be a burden to the doctor.
translation.value: 你紧张地对 <bot_18> 说你对医学一无所知，你不想成为医生的负担.

translation.key: For a moment, you have no idea how to react.
translation.value: 有那么一瞬间，你不知道该如何反应.

translation.key: You turn and see a Light Orb floating next to you. It emits a faint blue light. You have a feeling that's what was causing you to feel ill...
translation.value: 你转过身，看到一个光球漂浮在你旁边。它发出微弱的蓝光。你有一种感觉，那就是导致你不舒服的原因...

translation.key: "Something's appeared next to you. And, um, it's getting brighter..." <bot_23> tries his best to mask it, but you can tell he is worried.
translation.value: "你旁边出现了什么东西。嗯，天越来越亮了…..." <bot_23> 尽力掩饰，但你能看出他很担心.

translation.key: You take deep breaths to try to feel better, which seems to help. You start to feel lighter. As you fill your lungs with what... seems like more than just air.
translation.value: 你深呼吸，试着让自己感觉好一点，这似乎有帮助。你开始感觉轻松了。什么东西填满了你的肺…不只只是空气.

translation.key: Hey, <player>, what's wrong with you? Maybe we ought to induce vomiting...
translation.value: 嘿, <player>, 你怎么了?也许我们应该催吐...

translation.key: While Village <bot_23> is checking up on you, you start feeling nauseous.
translation.value: 当村民 <bot_23> 正在检查你的情况时，你开始感到恶心.

translation.key: Why do you feel dizzy? Could you be allergic to the medicine? Here, look. How many fingers am I holding up?
translation.value: 你为什么觉得头晕?你会不会对这种药过敏?看这里，（它举起了指头)这是几?

translation.key: What?! that medicine shouldn't have had any side effects. Let me take a closer look.
translation.value: 什么? !那种药应该不会有副作用的.让我仔细看看.

translation.key: To begin with, approach <bot_14>. She has something for you that will help your task.
translation.value: 首先，去找 <bot_14> .她有东西可以帮你完成任务.

translation.key: "Drink it up. It's the only way you'll have the energy to work tomorrow," <bot_23> says with a grin.
translation.value: "把它喝了吧,这是你明天有精力工作的唯一方法." <bot_23> 笑着说.

translation.key: Oh this <item_45>, a useful thing. At least for 3 days it will be easier.
translation.value: 噢，这是 <item_45> , 挺有用的，至少接下来三天可以轻松点.

translation.key: <bot_23> asked me to give this to you
translation.value: <bot_23> 让我把这个给你

translation.key: Wait until your mind stabilizes, then please send the potion to the lumberjacks.
translation.value: 等你的情绪稳定下来，再把药水送到伐木工人那里.

translation.key: I'll let you try this bottle of <item_45>. Trust me, it'll make you feel better.
translation.value: 试试这瓶 <item_45>. 相信我，这会让你感觉好些的.

translation.key: Good! Put them together and give 'em a good grind. Then mix in this medicine, bottle it, and we're done! Easy, eh?
translation.value: 非常好!把它们放在一起好好磨一磨。然后把药混在瓶子里，就完事了!很容易,不是吗?

translation.key:
"You are truly an excellent assistant," 

<bot_23> comments, patting you on the back.
translation.value:
"你是个十分优秀的助手," 

<bot_23>说，拍着你的背.

translation.key:
"Perfect! These are Skandia's most unique mushrooms." 

<bot_23> examines them out one by one.
translation.value:
"无与伦比！! 这简直是 Skandia 里最独特的蘑菇." 

<bot_23> 逐一检查了过去.

translation.key: I heard <bot_18> sent you here to help out. Luckily, I've got the perfect project for you.
translation.value: 我听说 <bot_18> 派你来帮忙。幸运的是，我为你准备了一个完美的项目.

translation.key: These mushrooms may well be Skandia's most valuable resource. A good deal of caravans come to the port just to buy them. I hear they are also excellent in risotto.
translation.value: 这些蘑菇是 Skandia 最有价值的东西. 很多商队来港口就是为了买这些东西。我听说他们做的意大利调味饭也很好吃.

translation.key:
<player>, looks like I need to ask you to go gather some <item_33>s. They typically grow near tree trunks. Take a look around the area, and I'm sure you'll find 'em.

(You can find the location of ores, loot, and mobs in the Wiki tab in the voting).
translation.value:
<player>, 看起来我需要让你去收集一些 <item_33>. 它们通常生长在树干附近[冒头的爱心就是]. 看看周围的区域，我相信你会找到他们.

(你可以在投票的Wiki标签中找到矿石，战利品和怪物的位置).

translation.key:
"I used up the mushrooms last time I prepared a medication. I haven't had time to seek them out again." 

<bot_23> scratches his head, anxious.
translation.value:
"我上次配药的时候把蘑菇都用光了。我还没来得及再去找他们." 

<bot_23> 抓着他的头，焦虑着.

translation.key:
"I've almost completely ground up these herbs. We should put some <item_33>s into the medicine and grind them together, too..." 

<bot_23> suddenly pauses to examine the medicine.
translation.value:
"我几乎把这些草药都磨碎了。我们应该把一些 <item_33> 放进药里，把它们一起磨碎..." 

<bot_23> 突然停下来检查药物.

translation.key: We used to have Aliya as an herbalist. I'm relying on you.
translation.value: Aliya 以前是我们的草药医生。但是现在你是我唯一的希望.

translation.key: I don't know why, but apparently he wants you to get all kinds of herbs for him.
translation.value: 我不知道为什么，但显然他想让你给他买各种草药.

translation.key: Oh yes, I was just waiting for you. <bot_23> asked me to give you this.
translation.value: 我正等你呢. <bot_23> 叫我给你这些b东西.

translation.key: Grass Pickaxe
translation.value: 草镐

translation.key: *You consider his reasoning, but it doesn't quite make sense. You explain to <bot_23> that perhaps your continuous nightmares have kept you from getting a proper night's sleep.*
translation.value: *你考虑了一下他的推理，但不太有道理。你向 <bot_23> 解释说，也许是你连续不断的噩梦让你晚上睡不好觉.*

translation.key: I'm going to officially name you as my assistant. When the time is right, I'll teach you everything I know! I bet you're a fast learner!
translation.value: 我要正式任命你为我的助理。等时机成熟，我会把我知道的一切都教给你!我打赌你学东西比索X克都快!

translation.key: *<bot_23> crows happily.*
translation.value: *<bot_23> 高兴地啼叫.*

translation.key: *You present <bot_23> with the <item_32> you collected.*
translation.value: *你给了 <bot_23> 所有你收集到的 <item_32> .*

translation.key: You need blood from <bot_24>s to make the refreshing medicine. Nothing's more invigorating than animal blood, am I right?
translation.value: 你需要 <bot_24> 的血液来制作提神药。没有什么比动物血更能提神了，对吧?

translation.key: I need you to prepare some <item_32> for me. You can find <bot_24> nearby.
translation.value: 我需要你给我准备点 <item_32> 给我，你可以在附近找到 <bot_24>.

translation.key: You and the other lumberjacks need something - some sort of medicine to refresh your minds and bodies. Something to put some pep back in your step.
translation.value: 你和其他伐木工人需要一些东西——某种药物来恢复你的精神和身体。能让你振作起来的东西.

translation.key: This should be a simple task for someone like you. Here, take this; it'll get your blood flowing.
translation.value: 这对你这样的人来说应该是一个简单的任务。来，拿着这个;这会让你血液循环变快.

translation.key: Something strange is happening to your body. You can feel the potion pumping through your every vein, and you also feel rather nauseous. You quickly explain your symptoms to <bot_23>.
translation.value: 你的身体发生了奇怪的变化。能感觉到药水在你的每根血管里流动，你感到很恶心.你迅速向 <bot_23> 解释现在的感觉.

translation.key: You must help me finish off today's work if you want your proper salary.
translation.value: 如果你想要拿到你的工资，你必须.

translation.key: At the moment, I can't find any physical problems. Maybe you're overworked; that can affect your brain, you know. You've got the same symptoms as the other workmen.
translation.value: 目前，我找不到任何身体问题。也许是你肾透支...呸，工作的太卖力了；你知道，这会影响你的大脑。你的症状和其他工人一样.

translation.key: <bot_18> sent you to me, I know.
translation.value: 我都懂，<bot_18> 派你过来找我

translation.key: Mm, okay.
translation.value: Mmm，好吧

translation.key: *You tell him how you're feeling today*
translation.value: *你告诉了他今天感觉如何*

translation.key: Hello, <player>, how are you?
translation.value: 嗨, <player>，最近怎么样？

translation.key: Haha, each of those lazy lumberjacks comes to me with the same complaints. Seems like this <bot_18> guy is pretty strict.
translation.value: 哈哈，每个懒惰的伐木工人都来找我抱怨同样的问题。看起来 <bot_18> 这个家伙很严格.

translation.key: Oh, c'mon. It can't be that hard! You only go to school for, what, eleven, twelve years to become a doctor? No biggie. Just look at it as a learning experience.
translation.value: 没有那么难！难不成你以为上了几年学就能成为一名合格的医生？不要紧，把这次经历当成一次实践吧

translation.key: I'm awake, don't touch me.
translation.value: 我醒着呢，别碰我！

translation.key: <player>, you have impressed me. I think I can recommend <bot_23> to you, you can make more money with it than working at the <world_1>.
translation.value: <player>, 你给我留下了深刻的印象，我可以把你推荐给 <bot_23> ,你可以跟着他在 <world_1> 赚更多的钱

translation.key: Fine, fine. I know I made a mistake. I won't do it again.
translation.value: 好吧，我知道我犯了个错误。我不会再犯了.

translation.key: "If you argue again, I'll take away your breaks," <bot_18> growls, glaring.
translation.value: "如果你再吵，我就剥夺你的休息时间," <bot_18> 瞪着眼睛咆哮着.

translation.key: You're such a scrooge! Everyone needs a nap now and again!
translation.value: 你这个吝啬鬼!每个人都需要时不时地打个盹!

translation.key: Not much of an excuse, you lazy fool! You only get half a day's pay today. End of discussion!
translation.value: 这可不是什么借口，你这个懒鬼!你今天只能拿到半天的工资!.讨论就此结束!

translation.key: I was just taking a break. I didn't know I was going to fall asleep. It's not a big deal.
translation.value: 我只是休息一下.不知道我会直接睡着.这没什么大不了的.

translation.key: See for yourself. <player>, who started working here just today, has contributed more to our project in one day than you have in your career. Shame on you!
translation.value: 看看你自己. <player>, 他今天才开始在这里工作，一天内对我们项目的贡献比你这辈子的贡献都多,你怎么敢的!

translation.key: You'll find a good deal of wood in the area. I need you to carry it to me.
translation.value: 你会在这个地区找到很多木头.我需要你把它带给我.

translation.key: Lately, numerous <bot_20>hops have migrated to the Logging Site. The naughty troublemakers make a mess all day long. Workmen complain constantly about picking up their, er, 'jelly beans.'
translation.value: 最近，很多 <bot_20> 到达了伐木场.整天在伐木场捣乱.工人们经常抱怨拿起他们的，呃，也许说是“糖豆”的东西?'

translation.key: You started to wake up the <bot_21>.
translation.value: 你叫醒 <bot_21>.

translation.key:
"Take this hammer and search the site for anyone sleeping on the job. Give 'em a wake up call they won't forget!"

 <bot_18> snarls, his face flushed with fury.
translation.value:
"拿着这把锤子，搜索一下现场有没有上班睡觉的人。给他们一个他们不会忘记的叫醒电话!"

 <bot_18> 咆哮着，他的脸因愤怒而涨得通红.

translation.key: <player>, everyone says I'm too harsh. I suppose you can judge for yourself now. Only you have returned with the wood. What are all the others doing out there, picking each other's noses?
translation.value: <player>, 我想你现在可以自己判断我是否是个苛刻的人.只有你带着木头回来了.其他人都在外面干什么，互相给对方挖鼻屎吗?

translation.key: What are those <bot_21> doing now? It's late, and they haven't brought the wood back yet.
translation.value: 那些 <bot_21> 现在在做什么?很晚了，他们还没把木头运回来.

translation.key: You move pretty fast. What about the others?
translation.value: 你走得倒挺快，别人呢？

translation.key: You pass the collected lumber to Caine.
translation.value: 你把收集到的木材交给了Caine.

translation.key: <bot_22> typically pile up the chopped wood under another tree. Take a walk around the Logging Site. It shouldn't be hard to find the wood.
translation.value: <bot_22> 通常将切碎的木头堆在另一棵树下.在伐木场周围走走.找到木头不难.

translation.key: These lazy fools are becoming more and more arrogant. It's time they take a pay cut! I doubt they'll dare slack off on the job again.
translation.value: 这些懒惰的傻瓜变得越来越傲慢了.该给他们减薪了. 我很怀疑他们是否会继续在工作中摸鱼.

translation.key: Well, there's no time to lose. you should just start working right away.
translation.value: 好吧，没时间浪费了。你应该马上开始工作.

translation.key: You shake your head and tell her that none of the merchants have seen him today. Hearing this, <bot_10>'s irritation starts to turn to worry.
translation.value: 你摇了摇头，告诉她今天没有一个商人见过他.听到这个消息, <bot_10> 不再生气了，反而开始担忧起来.

translation.key:
"It's about time to send the chopped wood back to the village"

Caine explains, scanning the sky.
translation.value:
"是时候把砍好的木头云回村里了"

Caine 扫视着天空，解释道.

translation.key: This was originally <bot_19>'s job, but I think you ought to take his place. You're more responsible than he ever was. Go to the Garrison Captain. I will speak to him.
translation.value: 最开始应该是 <bot_19> 的工作, 但我认为你可以胜任它. 你比他更有责任感. 去找警长吧. 我会跟他说一声的.

translation.key:
"Not bad for a newbie."

 <bot_18> is clearly satisfied by the reduced number of <bot_20>hops.
translation.value:
"对一个新手来说做的不错."

 <bot_18> 对 <bot_20> 数量减少了很多感到很满意

translation.key:
"We have three days to deliver to the furniture shop. We cannot be late."

 <bot_18> snaps, scanning a list.
translation.value:
"我们有三天时间送到店铺. 别迟到了."

 <bot_18> 骂道.说着打开了一个清单.

translation.key: I've a task for you. Drive the <bot_20>hops out of the Logging Site so the lumberjacks can focus on their work!
translation.value: 我有个任务给你.把 <bot_20> 统统赶走，这样我的工人才能好好伐木!

translation.key: We cannot let those rascally rabbits slow us down. If the wood is not delivered to the village fast enough, construction there will be delayed.
translation.value: 我们不能让那些流氓兔子拖我们的后腿.如果木材不能及时送到村里，那里的建设就会延误.

translation.key: Default
translation.value: 默认

translation.key:
"Jam! At last! My toast has been going naked!"

 <bot_15> pops open the jar, dips in his fingers, and slurps up the jelly eagerly.
translation.value:
"果酱! 终于! 我已经把面包的衣服脱光了!就等你这个!"

 <bot_15>打开罐子, 用手指蘸了蘸, 急切地吸了一口果冻.

translation.key: You shake your head and explain that you don't know him.
translation.value: 你摇摇头，解释说你不认识他.

translation.key: Speaking of which, have you seen <bot_19> lately? He hasn't come to work in days!
translation.value: 说到这里， 你最近看到过 <bot_19> 吗? 他好几天没来上班了!

translation.key: Did <bot_16> ask you to come here? Excellent. I was just wondering what the Garrison Members in the village normally do during the day. They just hang about the forest. They might as well be here doing something productive for once.
translation.value:
是 <bot_16> 叫你来的吗? 太好了.我只是想知道村里的驻军在白天通常都做些什么.
他们只是在森林里摸鱼,他们还不如在这里干点有意义的事.

translation.key:
"This boy <bot_19> is a fool! He only makes work harder for me! Unless we're short workers, I'd fire him right away!"

 <bot_18> grumbles to himself. It seems that working at the Logging Site is quite arduous.
translation.value:
"<bot_19> 纯纯傻瓜! 他只会让我工作更辛苦!除非我们人手不够，否则我会马上解雇他!"

 <bot_18> 自言自语道.看来在伐木场工作很辛苦.

translation.key: <player>, would you like to try working at the Logging Site? The salary's not bad.
translation.value: <player>, 你想在伐木场工作吗?薪水还不错.

translation.key: I didn't forget. But working for <bot_18> is no picnic. Very few are willing to work backbreaking hours at the Logging Site, and <bot_18>'s not exactly Mr. Personality.
translation.value: 我没有忘记.但是给 <bot_18> 打工不轻松. 很少有人愿意在伐木场好好伐木, 而且 <bot_18> 完全不是“先生”的性格.

translation.key: <bot_16>, you said you needed someone to replace one of <bot_18>'s... less enthusiastic workers. How could you forget so quickly?
